title: MORE OF THE SCORE - OCT. 16
text:
MORE OF THE SCORE - OCT. 16 
By DONOVAN KLEIN - 21ALIVE October 17, 2015 Updated Oct 17, 2015 at 12:30 AM EDT 
FORT WAYNE, IND (21ALIVE) - On the Oct. 16 episode of More of the Score, 21Alive's Kent Hormann and AWP's Antoine Taylor break down the big games around the area from the final week of regular season high school football. 
Coach Sherwood Haydock from Woodlan and Coach Luke Amstutz from East Noble call into the show to discuss their teams big wins and how far they will go into the post season.
